title: Man found dehydrated and sunburnt after disappearing 2 weeks in Australian tropical wilderness
text:
Published By: Fox News: World - Today 
Police say a 60-year-old man has been found two weeks after he disappeared in crocodile habitat in Australia's tropical wilderness....
